  },
  "summary": "Binary columnar, pipe-delimited TPC-H SF10. No data sorting (HDD sequential read prioritized). Zone maps on lineitem.l_shipdate and orders.o_orderdate for range filter pruning. Multi-value hash on lineitem.l_orderkey and orders.o_custkey for FK joins. Single-value hash on PK columns (orders, customer, part, supplier). Composite hash on partsupp(ps_partkey,ps_suppkey). DECIMAL as double. String columns: raw_char for CHAR(1), dictionary-int8 for low-cardinality, fixed-char arrays for output strings."
}
